				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Minh-B%E1%BB%95n-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/Ho%C3%A0i-T%E1%BB%8Bnh-th%E1%BB%95-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-XQeIMdWhHe2IeDJ_yTzFqA">Hoài Tịnh thổ thi kỳ 2 - 懷凈土詩其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Minh-B%E1%BB%95n-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-68uEHAKs3fNroOkYHc81FQ">Minh Bổn thiền sư</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-Bang-Ng%E1%BA%A1n/Ho%C3%A1n-kh%C3%AA-sa-L%C3%A2u-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-t%C3%ACnh-thi%C3%AAn-b%C3%ADch-t%E1%BB%A9-thu%E1%BB%B3/poem-tq4pdhUhQK1U_1EKcVeCoQ">Hoán khê sa (Lâu thượng tình thiên bích tứ thuỳ) - 浣溪沙（樓上晴天碧四垂）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-Bang-Ng%E1%BA%A1n/author-aRbK_iKDMX5ibYXonb22rA">Chu Bang Ngạn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-D%C6%B0/Khuy%E1%BA%BFn-nh%C4%A9-t%C3%B2ng-t%C6%B0/poem-U0010eUPFwoNEiH9M7Hztw">Khuyến nhĩ tòng tư - 勸爾從茲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-D%C6%B0/author-jwIeMxg44qgv_V08xi02Hw">Trần Ngọc Dư</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%C3%B9ng-Duy%C3%AAn-K%E1%BB%B7/Phao-c%E1%BA%A7u-l%E1%BA%A1c-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-7gIwd11XZQ5L5ywNcaNDWg">Phao cầu lạc kỳ 2 - 拋球樂其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%C3%B9ng-Duy%C3%AAn-K%E1%BB%B7/author-NkGwR6r3M3j5cQXaNNhfvQ">Phùng Duyên Kỷ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Phi%E1%BA%BFm-giang-t%E1%BB%91ng-kh%C3%A1ch/poem-IkRVAAufl45s4njuxafcJg">Phiếm giang tống khách - 泛江送客</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-th%C3%B9-Ti%E1%BA%BFt-th%E1%BA%ADp-nh%E1%BB%8B-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-ph%C3%A1n-quan-ki%E1%BA%BFn-t%E1%BA%B7ng/poem-KSb6ARCjcVZqO2cdc1bELQ">Phụng thù Tiết thập nhị trượng phán quan kiến tặng - 奉酬薛十二丈判官見贈</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/S%C6%A1n-th%C3%B4n-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-YDdB6yiSPv-5rnB5tYhVvQ">Sơn thôn kỳ 2 - 山村其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%91ng-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-th%E1%BA%ADp-ng%C5%A9-ph%C3%A1n-quan-ph%C3%B9-th%E1%BB%8B-ho%C3%A0n-Ki%E1%BB%81m-Trung-%C4%91%E1%BA%AFc-khai-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-8YXOeoyNJfJKeuGwOcXFtQ">Tống Vương thập ngũ phán quan phù thị hoàn Kiềm Trung, đắc khai tự - 送王十五判官扶侍還黔中，得開字</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/X%C3%A1-%C4%91%E1%BB%87-Quan-ph%C3%B3-Lam-%C4%90i%E1%BB%81n-th%E1%BB%A7-th%C3%AA-t%E1%BB%AD-%C4%91%C3%A1o-Giang-L%C4%83ng-h%E1%BB%89-k%C3%BD-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-OE-pDpto6-6GBYga41879A">Xá đệ Quan phó Lam Điền thủ thê tử đáo Giang Lăng, hỉ ký kỳ 3 - 舍弟觀赴藍田取妻子到江陵，喜寄其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Y%E1%BA%BFn-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-s%E1%BB%A9-qu%C3%A2n-tr%E1%BA%A1ch-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-EDcLwAG-ht_UVde0ajQdDA">Yến Vương sứ quân trạch đề kỳ 2 - 宴王使君宅題其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
